A man has died following a rescue operation off the Sussex coast.Police said they were called by HM Coastguard to east Brighton following reports a diver had been rescued from the sea.The coastguard helicopter was also deployed.Sussex Police confirmed a man in his 50s was taken to hospital where he was confirmed dead. The next of kin have been informed.
